      <li><strong>layout-sidebar:</strong> Stacks on narrow viewports</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>Accessibility Checklist</h3>
    <ul>
      <li>Use semantic HTML elements (<code>&lt;nav&gt;</code>, <code>&lt;main&gt;</code>, <code>&lt;section&gt;</code>)</li>
      <li>Add <code>aria-label</code> to navigation landmarks</li>
      <li>Use <code>aria-current="page"</code> for current navigation items</li>
      <li>Include <code>alt</code> text for images</li>
      <li>Ensure form fields have associated <code>&lt;label&gt;</code> elements</li>
    </ul>

